Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.66,0:01:31.77,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}爱慕…深深相爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.03,0:01:38.09,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}激情 干渴若狂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.85,0:01:40.92,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}阖上双目
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.08,0:01:44.36,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}罪孽深重
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.22,0:01:47.27,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.07,0:01:58.24,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}你的气味 令人发狂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.88,0:02:02.24,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}真夜中醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.24,0:02:05.40,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}疯狂 爱 一并饮干
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.40,0:02:08.44,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}投入这臂弯中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.44,0:02:11.60,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}"那边的黑暗是苦涩的"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.62,0:02:17.37,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}你惶然不知所措
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.03,0:02:21.00,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}即将要迎来永恒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.12,0:02:24.25,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}"这边的黑暗是甜美的"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:30.47,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}我深深地刺入
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.62,0:02:33.64,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}投入这臂弯中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.65,0:02:36.88,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}"那边的黑暗是苦涩的"
